text: Adnan Alkateb (عدنان الكاتب; born in 1958 in Latakia), is a British journalist of Syrian origin. He currently resides in Dubai and is the editorial Manager of Hia Magazine. == References == # Adnan AlKateb on writing Encyclopedia of Celebrities. AL-Quds Newspaper.
